Bryan O'Byrne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bryan_O%27Byrne 0 Bryan Jay O'Byrne (6 February 1931 – 4 December 2009) was an American film and television character actor and acting coach. His credits include numerous television shows, films and many television commercials.
